# DriveSafe AI — API Keys Configuration Template
# Copy this file to '.env' and fill in your actual API keys.

# 1. Gemini API Key (Required for live AI telemetry analysis)
# Obtain from Google AI Studio: https://aistudio.google.com/
GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSyYourGeminiApiKeyHere

# 2. Google Maps API Key (Optional, fallback is OpenStreetMap)
# Obtain from Google Cloud Console: https://console.cloud.google.com/
NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=AIzaSyYourGoogleMapsApiKeyHere
